(37, 'Acer Aspire 3 Laptop AMD Ryzen™ 3 7320U Quad-Core Processor (8 GB/512 GB SSD)', 'Laptop', 43999.00, 'Acer Aspire 3 Laptop - New Laptop\r\nThe Acer Aspire 3 15 is a sleek and powerful laptop designed for everyday computing needs. With a 15.6-inch Full HD display (1920 x 1080 pixels), it delivers crisp visuals and an immersive viewing experience.\r\n\r\nPerformance & Storage\r\nPowered by an AMD Ryzen 3 processor with a clock speed of 2.4 GHz, this laptop ensures smooth performance for multitasking, browsing, and productivity tasks. It features 8GB LPDDR5 RAM for efficient processing and 512GB SSD storage, providing ample space for files, applications, and a faster boot-up experience.\r\n\r\nGraphics & Audio\r\nEquipped with AMD integrated graphics, the Aspire 3 is capable of handling everyday graphical tasks, streaming, and casual gaming. The built-in speakers enhance your audio experience, making it perfect for entertainment and video calls.\r\n\r\nConnectivity & Battery Life\r\nStay connected with Bluetooth support and seamless wireless connectivity. The laptop is powered by a 40Wh lithium-ion battery with 3 cells, ensuring decent battery life for extended use on the go.\r\n\r\nBuild & Design\r\nWeighing 1.78 kg, the slim silver design makes it a stylish yet portable choice for students and professionals alike. The laptop operates on Windows 11 Home, offering a modern and user-friendly experience.\r\n\r\nPackage Contents\r\nAcer Aspire 3 Laptop\r\nPower Cord & Adapter\r\nUser Manual\r\nIdeal For:\r\n✔ Students & Professionals\r\n✔ Everyday Work & Entertainment\r\n✔ Light Gaming & Multimedia\r\n\r\nAcer Aspire 3 is a reliable laptop with a balance of performance, portability, and affordability, making it an excellent choice for users looking for a solid computing experience.', '9818559036', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dcrk1fzah/image/upload/v1740828039/wjdolg1vwblvruf3srka.png', '2025-03-01 11:20:39'),
(38, 'Apple MacBook Air A1466 13.3-inch Laptop (Core i7/8GB/128GB/Sierra/Integrated Graphics), Silver', 'Laptop', 38500.00, 'Apple MacBook Air A1466 (Refurbished) – Lightweight & Reliable Performance\r\nThe Apple MacBook Air A1466 (2015) is a sleek, ultra-portable laptop designed for productivity and everyday use. With its lightweight aluminum body, long battery life, and smooth macOS experience, this refurbished model is a great choice for students, professionals, and casual users looking for a budget-friendly MacBook.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\n📺 Display & Design\r\n13.3-inch LED-backlit widescreen display with a 1440 x 900 resolution, delivering crisp visuals and vibrant colors.\r\nSlim & lightweight design (weighing just 1.35 kg) makes it easy to carry anywhere.\r\n⚡ Performance & Storage\r\n5th Gen Intel Core i5 dual-core processor ensures smooth performance for everyday tasks.\r\nIntel HD Graphics 6000 for seamless web browsing, streaming, and light creative work.\r\nComes with 4GB or 8GB LPDDR3 RAM for efficient multitasking.\r\nStorage options include 128GB or 256GB PCIe-based SSD, ensuring fast boot-up and app performance.\r\n🔗 Connectivity & Ports\r\nUSB 3.0 (x2), Thunderbolt 2, MagSafe 2 charging port, and SDXC card slot for seamless connectivity.\r\n3.5mm headphone jack for audio convenience.\r\n802.11ac Wi-Fi & Bluetooth 4.0 for wireless connectivity.\r\n🔋 Battery & Operating System\r\nUp to 12 hours of battery life for web browsing and media playback.\r\nOriginally shipped with macOS Yosemite (10.10), but supports later macOS versions for updated features.\r\n🔧 Warranty & Condition\r\nRefurbished & Tested for quality assurance.\r\nComes with a 1-month testing warranty.\r\n', '9818559036', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dcrk1fzah/image/upload/v1740828232/k4s7kggf3gxqv7xv7spz.png', '2025-03-01 11:23:52'),
(39, 'Apple MacBook Pro A1502 13.3-inch Laptop (Intel Core i5/8GB/256GB SSD/Mac OS/Integrated Graphics), Silver', 'Laptop', 23645.00, 'Apple MacBook Pro A1502 (Refurbished) – Powerful Performance with Retina Display\r\nThe Apple MacBook Pro A1502 (2013, Refurbished) is a high-performance laptop designed for professionals, students, and creative users. Featuring a stunning Retina display, powerful Intel Core processors, and a sleek aluminum design, this MacBook Pro delivers smooth performance and reliability at an affordable price.\r\n\r\n🔹 Key Features:\r\n📺 Retina Display & Design\r\n13.3-inch Retina display with an ultra-sharp 2560 x 1600 resolution for vibrant colors and clear visuals.\r\nSleek aluminum body, lightweight, and easy to carry, weighing just 1.57 kg.\r\n⚡ Performance & Storage\r\nPowered by Intel Core i5/i7 (Haswell generation) dual-core processor, ensuring fast performance.\r\nIntegrated Intel Iris Graphics 5100 for smooth visuals, video editing, and creative work.\r\nConfigurations available with 4GB or 8GB DDR3L RAM for multitasking.\r\nPCIe-based SSD storage options: 128GB, 256GB, 512GB, or 1TB, ensuring fast boot times and quick data access.\r\n🔗 Connectivity & Ports\r\n2 x USB 3.0 ports for fast data transfer.\r\n2 x Thunderbolt 2 ports for high-speed connectivity.\r\n1 x HDMI port for external display support.\r\n1 x SDXC card slot & 3.5mm headphone jack for added convenience.\r\nMagSafe 2 power port for secure charging.\r\n📡 Wireless & Operating System\r\n802.11ac Wi-Fi & Bluetooth 4.0 for seamless connectivity.\r\nOriginally shipped with macOS Mavericks (10.9) but supports newer macOS versions.\r\n🔋 Battery Life & Warranty\r\nUp to 9 hours of web browsing or video playback.\r\nRefurbished & tested with a 1-month testing warranty.\r\n', '9818559036', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dcrk1fzah/image/upload/v1740828473/mivxokdb0rf6qv9r8bal.png', '2025-03-01 11:27:54'),
