(52, 'Dell Latitude E5310 Core i5 | 10th Generation | Window 11 Pro | 13.3″ Screen', 'Laptop', 23000.00, 'Dell Latitude E5310 – Compact, Powerful & Business-Ready\r\nThe Dell Latitude E5310 is a business-class laptop designed for professionals who require performance, portability, and security. Equipped with Intel Core i5/i7 processors, up to 32GB RAM, and fast SSD storage, this 13.3-inch compact laptop delivers exceptional speed, efficiency, and enterprise-grade security features, making it ideal for on-the-go professionals and remote workers.\r\n\r\n🔹 Key Features:\r\n⚡ High-Speed Performance & Productivity\r\n10th/11th Gen Intel Core i5 or i7 Processor – Ensures smooth multitasking and high-speed processing.\r\nUp to 32GB DDR4 RAM – Enhances efficiency and handles heavy workloads effortlessly.\r\nSSD Storage (256GB to 1TB Options) – Provides lightning-fast boot times and ample storage for files and applications.\r\n📺 Crisp & Vibrant Display\r\n13.3-inch Full HD (1920 x 1080) Display – Delivers sharp visuals with anti-glare technology for comfortable viewing.\r\nIPS Panel Available – Provides wider viewing angles and superior color accuracy.\r\n🎮 Integrated Graphics & Performance\r\nIntel UHD Graphics or Iris Xe (Varies by CPU) – Delivers smooth performance for multimedia, office work, and video conferencing.\r\n4K Support Available – Perfect for high-resolution displays and external monitor setups.\r\n🔗 Advanced Connectivity & Ports\r\nWi-Fi 6 & Bluetooth 5.1 – Ensures fast and stable wireless connectivity.\r\nMultiple Ports for Maximum Versatility:\r\nUSB Type-C & USB 3.2 – For fast data transfer and device connectivity.\r\nHDMI Port – Easily connect to external monitors and projectors.\r\nEthernet Port – Stable and secure wired internet connection.\r\nHeadphone/Microphone Combo Jack – For seamless audio communication.\r\n🔒 Enterprise-Grade Security Features\r\nFingerprint Reader & IR Camera (Optional) – Secure login with Windows Hello facial recognition.\r\nTPM