(53, 'Dell Latitude E5400 Core i5 | 8th Generation | Win 11 pro', 'Laptop', 19000.00, 'Dell Latitude 5400 – Business-Class Performance & Security\r\nThe Dell Latitude 5400 is a powerful and reliable business laptop, designed for productivity, security, and efficiency. Featuring 8th Gen Intel Core i5 processors, up to 32GB RAM, and a Full HD anti-glare display, this laptop is perfect for professionals, students, and enterprise users looking for a durable and high-performance computing solution.\r\n\r\n🔹 Key Features:\r\n⚡ Fast & Efficient Performance\r\n8th Gen Intel Core i5-8265U Processor – Delivers excellent speed for multitasking and business applications.\r\nUp to 32GB DDR4 RAM – Handles multiple applications and high-performance tasks seamlessly.\r\nSSD Storage Options (128GB to 512GB) – Fast boot times, quick data access, and ample storage for work and files.\r\n📺 Crisp Full HD Display\r\n14-inch Full HD (1920 x 1080) Anti-Glare Display – Provides sharp visuals with reduced eye strain.\r\nOptional Touchscreen Configurations – Enhances interactivity and user experience.\r\n🎮 Integrated Graphics & Performance\r\nIntel UHD Graphics 620 – Ensures smooth video playback, light editing, and office tasks.\r\n4K Support – Allows connection to high-resolution external displays.\r\n🔗 Advanced Connectivity & Ports\r\nUSB-C with DisplayPort Support – Fast data transfer and display connectivity.\r\nUSB 3.1 Gen 1 Ports – High-speed file transfer and peripheral connection.\r\nHDMI & Ethernet Port – Easy external display setup and stable wired internet connection.\r\nHeadphone/Microphone Combo Jack & SD Card Reader – For versatile multimedia needs.\r\n🔒 Enterprise-Grade Security Features\r\nFingerprint Reader & SmartCard Reader – Provides secure access and authentication.\r\nTPM 2.0 (Trusted Platform Module) – Enhances data security and encryption.\r\nHD Webcam with Privacy Shutter – Ensures security and protection against unauthorized access.\r\n🔋 Long-Lasting Battery Life\r\