(54, 'Dell Latitude e5410 Core i5 Processor | 10th Generation | Win 11 Pro', 'Laptop', 22899.00, 'Dell Latitude 5410 – Powerful Business Laptop for Professionals\r\nThe Dell Latitude 5410 is a sleek, high-performance business laptop designed for professionals, students, and remote workers. Equipped with an Intel Core i5 processor, Full HD display, SSD storage, and enterprise-grade security, this 14-inch laptop delivers fast performance, durability, and efficiency, making it an excellent choice for productivity and multitasking.\r\n\r\n🔹 Key Features:\r\n⚡ Reliable Performance & Speed\r\nIntel Core i5 Processor (1.7 GHz) – Ensures smooth performance for business applications, multitasking, and productivity.\r\n8GB DDR4 RAM (Expandable up to 16GB, 2400 MHz) – Handles multiple applications and improves efficiency.\r\n256GB SSD Storage – Delivers fast boot times and quick access to files and applications.\r\n📺 Full HD Display & Compact Design\r\n14-inch Full HD (1920 x 1080) Display – Provides sharp visuals and vibrant colors for an immersive experience.\r\nCompact & Lightweight (1.47 kg) – Designed for portability and easy handling.\r\n🎮 Graphics & Audio\r\nIntel UHD Graphics 620 (Integrated) – Supports smooth video playback and light graphics work.\r\nBuilt-in Speakers – Delivers clear audio for calls, presentations, and entertainment.\r\n🔗 Connectivity & Ports\r\nWi-Fi Connectivity – Ensures fast and stable internet connections.\r\nMultiple Ports for Enhanced Productivity:\r\nUSB Ports – For external devices and fast data transfer.\r\nHDMI Port – Connect to external displays and projectors.\r\nNo Optical Drive – Slimmer and more lightweight design.\r\n🔒 Security & Enterprise Features\r\nWindows 10 Pro Preloaded – Business-friendly OS with enhanced security and productivity tools.\r\nEnterprise-Grade Security – Ideal for professional and business use.\r\n🔋 Battery & Power Efficiency\r\nBattery-Powered with 4.9Wh Lithium Battery – Ensures extended work sessions.\r\n45W