(55, 'Dell Latitude e5420 (Core i5-11th Gen Processor | 14Inch Display | Win 11 Pro)', 'Laptop', 25800.00, 'Dell Latitude 5420 – Empower Your Productivity\r\nThe Dell Latitude 5420 is a business-class laptop designed for professionals, remote workers, and corporate users who need powerful performance, durability, and enterprise-level security. With its 11th Gen Intel Core i5 processor, Full HD anti-glare display, and long-lasting battery, this 14-inch laptop ensures seamless multitasking, fast data transfer, and superior security for modern work environments.\r\n\r\n🔹 Key Features:\r\n⚡ High-Speed Performance for Productivity\r\n11th Gen Intel Core i5-1135G7 Processor (Up to 4.2 GHz Turbo Boost, 4 Cores) – Delivers fast and efficient multitasking.\r\nUp to 32GB DDR4 RAM – Handles business applications, multitasking, and collaboration tools with ease.\r\nUp to 1TB PCIe NVMe SSD Storage – Provides lightning-fast boot times and ample storage for work files.\r\n📺 Crisp Full HD Display & Eye Comfort\r\n14-inch Full HD Anti-Glare Display (250 nits Brightness) – Offers sharp visuals and reduces eye strain during extended use.\r\n🎮 Advanced Graphics for Smooth Performance\r\nIntel Iris Xe Graphics (Integrated) – Supports smooth video playback, office applications, and light multimedia work.\r\n🔗 Advanced Connectivity & Ports\r\nWi-Fi 6 (802.11ax) & Bluetooth 5.1 – Ensures stable, fast wireless connections.\r\nMultiple Ports for Enhanced Productivity:\r\n2x USB 3.2 Type-A – Fast data transfer and peripheral connection.\r\n2x USB Type-C with Thunderbolt 4 – For ultra-fast data transfer and external display support.\r\nHDMI 1.4 & RJ-45 Ethernet Port – Reliable wired internet and multi-monitor setup.\r\nMicroSD Card Reader – Expandable storage and easy file transfers.\r\n🔒 Enterprise-Level Security Features\r\nFingerprint Reader & IR Camera for Windows Hello (Optional) – Secure biometric authentication.\r\nTPM 2.0 (Trusted Platform Module) – Encrypts sensitive data for enhanced