(56, 'Dell Latitude E5440 laptop (Corei5/4th Gen/8GB/256GB)', 'Laptop', 18500.00, 'Dell Latitude E5440 (Refurbished) – Reliable & Business-Ready\r\nThe Dell Latitude E5440 is a refurbished business-class laptop designed for productivity, reliability, and security. Originally released in 2013, this 14-inch laptop is ideal for office professionals, students, and everyday users looking for an affordable, durable, and efficient computing solution.\r\n\r\n🔹 Key Features:\r\n⚡ Dependable Performance\r\nIntel Core i3 / i5 / i7 (4th Gen Haswell) – Delivers solid performance for everyday tasks.\r\n4GB to 8GB DDR3L RAM (Expandable Options Available) – Handles multitasking efficiently.\r\nStorage Options:\r\nHDD (320GB to 1TB) – More space for files and media.\r\nSSD (128GB to 256GB) – Faster boot times and application performance.\r\n📺 Compact & Clear Display\r\n14-inch Anti-Glare LED-Backlit Display – Reduces eye strain and enhances visibility.\r\nHD Resolution (1366 x 768 Pixels) – Clear and sharp visuals for daily computing.\r\n🎮 Graphics & Multimedia\r\nIntegrated Intel HD Graphics – Supports basic graphical tasks and video playback.\r\nBuilt-in Speakers & Audio Jack – Delivers clear audio for calls and media.\r\n🔗 Connectivity & Ports\r\nUSB 3.0 & USB 2.0 Ports – For faster data transfer.\r\nHDMI & VGA Ports – Connect to external displays easily.\r\nEthernet Port (RJ-45) & Wi-Fi (802.11a/b/g/n) – Reliable wired and wireless internet connectivity.\r\nBluetooth Support – Connects wirelessly to peripherals.\r\nSD Card Reader & Headphone/Microphone Combo Jack – Versatile connectivity for external devices.\r\n🔒 Business-Grade Security Features\r\nFingerprint Reader (Optional) – Secure and easy login.\r\nTPM (Trusted Platform Module) – Protects sensitive business data.\r\nSmart Card Reader (Optional) – Adds an extra layer of security for corporate use.\r\n🔋 Battery & Power Efficiency\r\nLong-Lasting Battery Life – Designed for all-day productivity on the go.\r\n💻 Preloaded Operating System\r\nWindows 7 / Windows 8 (Upgradeable to Windows 10) – Familiar and efficient OS for business and home use.\r\n', '9818559036', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dcrk1fzah/image/upload/v1740833596/ylbjqdhmko1zuut61r3t.png', '2025-03-01 12:53:17');
