(27, 'Social Media Manager', 'Petnojo', 'Spaze i-Tech Park, Gurugram, India', 45000, 50000, 'Full Time', '3 - 4 years', 'High School', 'We are seeking a creative and strategic Social Media Manager to oversee our company\'s social media presence. The ideal candidate will have 3–4 years of experience in managing social media platforms, developing engaging content, and driving brand awareness. This role requires a deep understanding of social media trends, excellent communication skills, and the ability to analyze metrics to inform strategy.\r\n\r\nKey Responsibilities:\r\nStrategy Development: Create and implement comprehensive social media strategies aligned with business goals.​\r\nContent Creation: Develop, curate, and manage engaging content across various platforms, including Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, LinkedIn, and YouTube.​\r\nCommunity Management: Engage with followers, respond to comments and messages promptly, and foster a positive community.​\r\nAnalytics and Reporting: Monitor, analyze, and report on performance metrics, adjusting strategies as needed to optimize engagement and reach.​\r\nCollaboration: Work closely with the marketing team to ensure brand consistency and support promotional campaigns.​\r\nTrend Monitoring: Stay updated on the latest social media trends, tools, and best practices, incorporating them into strategies.\r\n\r\nQualifications:\r\nEducation: Bachelor’s degree in Marketing, Communications, or a related field.​\r\nExperience: 3–4 years of proven experience in social media management.​\r\n\r\nSkills:\r\nProficiency in social media platforms and tools (e.g., Hootsuite, Buffer, Canva).​\r\nStrong writing, editing, and communication skills.​\r\nAbility to analyze data and derive actionable insights.​\r\nCreative thinking and problem-solving abilities.​\r\nKnowledge of SEO and web traffic metrics.\r\n\r\nPreferred Qualifications:\r\nExperience with paid social media advertising campaigns.​\r\nFamiliarity with graphic design and video editing tools.​\r\nCertification in Digital Marketing or Social Media Management.', 'Media, Arts & Entertainment', 2, 1, '', 'Spaze i-Tech Park, Gurugram, India', '', 5, '9', 1, 0, '2025-04-11 07:04:11', NULL),
(28, 'Telecaller', 'sortout innovation', 'Spaze i-Tech Park, Gurugram, India', 20000, 25000, 'Full Time', '1 - 2 years', 'High School', 'We are seeking an enthusiastic and articulate Telecaller fluent in Kannada and English to join our dynamic team. The ideal candidate will be responsible for handling inbound and outbound calls, addressing customer inquiries, and promoting our products/services. This role demands excellent communication skills and a customer-centric approach.\r\n\r\nKey Responsibilities:\r\nMake outbound calls to potential and existing customers to inform them about our products/services.​\r\nHandle inbound customer inquiries and provide appropriate solutions.​\r\nMaintain a database of customer information and update it regularly.​\r\nFollow up with customers to ensure their satisfaction and address any concerns.​\r\nAchieve daily and monthly call targets set by the management.​\r\nCollaborate with the sales and marketing teams to enhance customer engagement.\r\n\r\nQualifications:\r\nEducation: Minimum of a Bachelor\'s degree or equivalent.​\r\nExperience: 1–2 years in a telecalling or customer service role.​\r\nLanguage Proficiency: Fluent in Kannada and English (both verbal and written).​\r\n\r\nSkills:\r\nExcellent communication and interpersonal skills.​\r\nProficiency in using telecalling software and CRM systems.​\r\nAbility to handle rejection and stress in soliciting customers.​\r\nStrong organizational and multitasking abilities.\r\n\r\nPreferred Qualifications:\r\nExperience in the logistics or related industry.​\r\nKnowledge of additional regional languages is a plus.​\r\nCertification in customer service or sales training programs.​', 'Sales & Business Development', 4, 1, '', 'Spaze i-Tech Park, Gurugram, India', '', 6, '9', 1, 0, '2025-04-11 07:08:45', NULL),
